<英文法規名稱>Regulations Governing the Accounting Treatment and Preparation of Financial Reports for Foundations Overseen by the Central Bank of the Republic of China (Taiwan)</英文法規名稱>
<中文法規名稱>中央銀行主管財團法人會計處理及財務報告編製準則</中文法規名稱>
